        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-01-13 21:23:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6: Code-Review-1\n\nAndrew I give you huge kudos for mastering JJB so thoroughly and quickly.  But my main concern remains, you must be able to create jobs for multiple branches, at least master and the most recently released version.  I don't know if I'm reading your YAML correctly, it appears that the branch name must be set as a string, rather than chosen from a list as is done elsewhere, and because of that I feel forced to vote -1.",
        "patchset_number": 6
