        "timestamp": "2020-01-13 21:51:24.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nChris, I tried adding a second stream/branch, in my local environment, and looked at what changed in the results of running jenkins-jobs test, to make sure it makes sense.  You get docker-merge and docker-verify jobs for the additional streams with the correct branch, which is what is expected.  The other 5 jobs shouldn't be duplicated, and they aren't.",
